[Student "S"]
{SOUTH's 3\D bid is Fourth Suit Forcing and 
does NOT show a \D stopper.

The bid asks NORTH to further describe her hand. 
NORTH does not have a rebiddable suit, but does have \Ds stopped so she bids 3NT.}

