[Student "S"]
{WEST cannot rebid the 5-card \S suit, cannot support EAST's \Ds, 
and cannot bid Notrump without a \H stopper.

So she bids 3\C, New Minor Forcing, asking EAST to describe his hand further.

EAST doesn't have three \Ss, nor does he have four \Hs. 
But he does have \Hs stopped, so bids 2NT. West is not strong 
enough to bid game so she passes.}

